# Android Notification Sound Files
#
# Place custom MP3 files here before releasing to the Play Store.
# When files are present, update NotificationSoundConfig.kSoundFilesPresent
# to true in lib/core/services/notification_sound_config.dart.
#
# Required filenames (exact — case-sensitive):
#   adhan.mp3            — Full adhan for the five daily prayers
#   iftar_adhan.mp3      — Iftar adhan at Maghrib during Ramadan
#   quran_reminder.mp3   — Gentle Quran recitation for reading reminders
#   habit_reminder.mp3   — Optional soft tone for habit check-ins
#   general_reminder.mp3 — Optional soft tone for general notifications
#
# Sources (free, royalty-free):
#   https://www.islamicfinder.org/prayer-times/
#   https://zekr.org/
#   https://al-quran.cloud/ (Islamic Network API)
#
# Until files are present, all notifications use the device's default
# notification sound — the app works correctly with no files here.
